classification.tableDescription: 1965-70 Modified Basic Table – Male. Basis: Age Last Birthday. Minimum Select Age: 0. Maximum Select Age: 70. Minimum Ultimate Age: 15. Maximum Ultimate Age: 99
classification.comments: Study Data: Built from the Modified 1965-70 Basic Table (See SOA Table Identities 1610 and 1611). Methodology: Mortality rates on an age last birthday basis were calculated not by obtaining mean mortality rates from the age nearest birthday rates but rather by developing a select and ultimate lx, setting the radix equal to 1,000,000. A four-step process was followed to then arrive at the age- last birthday rates. This approach is similar to that followed in construction of the Commissioners Standard Ordinary (CSO) 1958 Mortality Tables on an age last birthday basis. Data Transcription Errors: None.  Data Certified: 03/2013
